    end

    SHELL["Shell"] --- P_DNA
    CORE["Core"] --- V_DNA
    EXPERT["Expert"] --- ROLE & SKILL & RULE
    DEV["Dev"] --- ROLE & SKILL & STYLE & EXP
    REVIEW["Review"] --- ROLE & RULE & EXP
```

### Prompt 块存储

```
prompts/
├── dna/                          # 🔒 不可变
│   ├── shell_persona.md
│   └── core_values.md
├── roles/                        # 🧩 原子化
│   ├── backend_expert.md
│   ├── frontend_expert.md
│   └── code_reviewer.md
├── skills/
│   ├── python_ast.md
│   └── nginx_ops.md
├── styles/
│   └── code_with_tests.md
└── rules/
    └── conventional_commit.md
```

### 组装与修改权限

- Expert spawn Dev 时**自由挑选原子块**组装 prompt + 自动注入相关经验
- **Core** 可修改所有原子块（受审批链约束）
- **Expert** 可修改自己域内的技能/风格块
- **Dev/Review** 只能**建议修改**（`report_to_parent`）

```python
spawn_child_agent(
    role="dev",
    prompt_blocks=["roles/backend.md", "skills/python_ast.md", "styles/code_with_tests.md"],
    # + 框架自动注入 memory/ 中检索到的经验块
)
```

